high_descs: Turn to the left, walk to the microwave above the sink.
Take the apple out of the microwave.
Step in front of the small sink.
Put the apple in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water after washing the apple, pick up the apple.
Step in front of the big sink.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the clean apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left to go past the stove then turn left again to go towards the fridge. Make a right and go to the sink and look above at the microwave.
Open the microwave to take out the apple and shut the door.
Turn left and then right to go to the left side of the sink.
Put the apple on the right side of the sink. Fill the sink with water, turn it off then take the apple back out.
Turn to the right then a quick left to raise the apple up to the microwave.
Place the apple inside the microwave on the right side of the plate and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: To clean an apple to put it back in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the microwave
Open the microwave, take the fruit out of the microwave, close the microwave
Walk to the left a little
Put the fruit in the sink on the right, turn on the faucet, wash the fruit, turn off the faucet, take the fruit
Walk to the right a little
Open the microwave, put the fruit back in, close the microwave
anns.task_desc: Wash the fruit from the microwave, put it back

high_descs: Turn left, move to in front of the microwave.
Pick up the apple from the microwave.
Turn left, move to in front of the sink.
Place the apple into the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to in front of the microwave.
Place the apple into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed apple into the microwave.
